A policy shows details about coverage, insured items, and insured parties. Go to the Policy list view, click the name of the policy you want to view. To view coverage attributes, click the coverage's bar. To view coverage and insured item details, click the gray carat on the right side of the bar and choose View Details.

You can also view details about Insured Items or Insured Parties on the Insured Items LWC tab. If this policy has insured parties listed as children of insured items, to view the insured party details click the name of the insured party.
